This paper is about a novel reinforcement learning method that involves planning in certain parts of the environment. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Robotics (cs.RO), Systems and Control (cs.SY), and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS).
